paathshaala ( hindi : पाठशाला ; school ) is a 2010 indian drama film that stars shahid kapoor , ayesha takia , shraddha arya , ali haji , sushant singh and nana patekar and is directed by milind ukey . the story revolves around children on a school campus . it comments on the indian education system and its shortcomings . kapoor plays an english and music teacher . it is inspired by the marathi film shaala , also directed by milind ukey . paathshaala opened on 16 april 2010 to mixed reviews .